  &lt;h3&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Summary
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;</content>
    <summary type="text">Let's go over the basics on how to edit and update your Duda Website. We will show you how to edit your Duda pages, content, text and images.</summary>
