  <entry>
    <title>Don’t Underestimate The Power Of Doorknocking</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="https://www.heliummarketing.agency/dont-underestimate-the-power-of-doorknocking" />
    <link rel="enclosure" type="image/png" href="https://irp.cdn-website.com/fad78d66/dms3rep/multi/Frame+10.png" length="49112" />
    <author>
      <name>Helium Marketing</name>
      <email>administrator@heliummarketing.agency (Helium Marketing)</email>
    </author>
    <updated>2021-07-14T05:31:40Z</updated>
    <published>2021-07-14T05:31:40Z</published>
    <content>&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;h2&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Why old-fashioned marketing strategies still work.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p style="line-height: 1.6;"&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           I recently joined 6PR’s 
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://www.6pr.com.au/show/perth-live-with-oliver-peterson/" target="_blank" style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Perth LIVE
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
            with Oliver Peterson to chat about where people should start when trying to get a new business off the ground. We talked all things marketing, like digital vs traditional and how to nurture your customers. And, we spontaneously gave away a free website on-air!
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p style="line-height: 1.6;"&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Listen to the podcast below.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span&gt;&#xD;
        
            ﻿
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           For help launching your new business, 
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/contact" style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           contact us
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           . We’ll chat about the right blend of traditional and digital marketing strategies and help you get off the ground.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;</content>
    <summary type="text">Ever thought about door knocking to increase the revenue of your business? Scott joins Oliver Petersen from 6PR to discuss how this worked for Helium.</summary>
